         <abstract id="aspace_3fe7dcee7b9e1dcb7b4044eb388c54a4">Chiefly printed copies of Serge Chermayeff's writings and research files on architecture. About half the papers consist of teaching materials from master class seminars in architecture conducted by Chermayeff at Yale University in 1966-1967.</abstract>
